title: Dinosaur Comics - Complete through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"DINOSAUR COMICS" Web Comic

"Dinosaur Comics" (qwantz.com) by Ryan North centers on three main characters, T-Rex, Utahraptor and Dromiceiomimus.  As a general rule, every strip uses the same artwork, with only the dialogue changing from day to day.  The strips take on a wide variety of topics, including ethical relativism, the nature of happiness, and the secret to being loved.


This torrent collects "Dinosaur Comics" comics.  (Yes, that sounds redundant.)  The comics are compiled into a set of CBR files, one for each year, starting with 2003 and running through 2014.  Each comic's page includes its number, title and mouseover text
